C-b  Move backward one char    C-f  Move forward one char
A-b  Move backward one word    A-f  Move forward one word
C-h  Delete backward           C-d  Delete forward
C-a  Jump to line beginning    C-e  Jump to line end
%
C-u  Cut cursor to line start  C-k  Cut cursor to line end
C-w  Cut word before cursor    A-d  Cut word after cursor
C-y  Paste last cut text       A-y  Paste second last cut text
A-C-y	Paste first argument of the previous command
A-./_	Paste last argument of the previous command
%
C-c  SIGINT (kill)             C-d  Send EOF (exit)
C-z  SIGSTOP (suspend)         fg   Resume suspened process
C-\  SIGQUIT                   C-l  Clear (or redraw) screen
S-PgUp  Scroll back a page     S-PgDown  Scroll down a page
%
C-p  Previous line in history  C-n  Next line in history
C-r  Reverse history search    C-s  Search history
C-j  End search                C-g  Abort search
A-r  Revert changes made
%
A-*  Echo completions          A-?  Pager completions
Tab  Completion
%
